Vietaâ€™s-Formula.content:
What is Vietaâ€™s Formula
What is Vietaâ€™s Formula
â†“

Sum of roots in Vietaâ€™s Formula
â†“
\begin{align}
r_{1}+r_{2}=-\frac{b}{a} \\
\end{align}

Product of roots in Vietaâ€™s Formula
â†“
\begin{align}
r_{1}r_{2}=\frac{c}{a}
\end{align}

Derive the Vietaâ€™s Formula
â†“
\begin{align}
a(x-r_{1})(x-r_{2}) &amp;= 0 \\
a(x^2-(r_{1}+r_{2})x+r_{1}r_{2}) &amp;= 0 \\
ax^2-a(r_{1}+r_{2})x+ar_{1}r_{2} &amp;= 0 \\
-a(r_{1}+r_{2}) = b &amp;\implies r_{1}+r_{2}=-\frac{b}{a} \\
ar_{1}r_{2} = c &amp;\implies r_{1}r_{2} = \frac{c}{a}
\end{align}

